*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Report ZNAM_INTER
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*&
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
REPORT ZNAM_INTER.

DATA: num1 TYPE i,
      num2 TYPE i,
      sum  TYPE i.

num1 = 2. num2 = 4.
PERFORM add_no USING num1 num2 CHANGING sum.
PERFORM rep_out USING num1 num2 sum.
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Form add_no
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& text
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*&      --> NUM1
*&      --> NUM2
*&      <-- SUM
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
FORM add_no  USING    p_num1
                      p_num2
             CHANGING p_sum.
  P_SUM = P_NUM1 + P_NUM2.

ENDFORM.
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Form rep_out
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& text
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*&      --> NUM1
*&      --> NUM2
*&      --> SUM
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
FORM rep_out  USING    p_num1
                       p_num2
                       p_sum.
  WRITE: / 'Sum of', p_num1, 'and', p_num2, 'is', p_sum.
ENDFORM.
